<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Dogfooding</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="<%= image_path("apple-touch-icon.png") %>" />
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>


<div class="container">
  <h1><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-cutlery"></span> Chilema.Today</h1>
  <h3>提示：当日确认无效，请提前一天确认是否取消用餐。</h3>
  <h3><%= flash[:notice] %></h3>
  <h3 style='color: red;'><%= flash[:alert] %></h3>
  
  <h4 class='text-info'> 今日午餐人数: <span class="badge"><%= today_lunch_count %></span></h4>
  <h4 class='text-info'> 今日晚餐人数: <span class="badge"><%= today_dinner_count %></span></h4>
  <hr />

  <%= yield %>
</div>

</body>
</html>
